            "id": 129295,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Programas são mais divertidos se puderem receber entrada do exterior.</p><p>Quando executamos o <code>code</code>, podemos incluir a entrada para alterar o programa.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Order",
            "id": 129296,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>A ordem das instruções importa. Uma vez que coletamos a entrada e a armazenamos em uma variável, podemos reutilizá-la.</p><p>Coloque as linhas na ordem correta para usar a saída coletada na instrução de saída.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;What's your name?&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"name_input = input()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Hi, \" /><text value=\"{name_input}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"!&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"75\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"What's your name?\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Mimo\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Hi, Mimo!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>name_input = input()</code> seguido de <code>print(f\"Hi, {name_input}!\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Console",
            "id": 129297,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para coletar a entrada de um usuário em um programa Python, usamos a função <code>input</code>. A entrada do usuário pode então ser atribuída a uma variável.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"user_input = input()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option startIndex=\"19\" endIndex=\"20\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>input</code> seguido de <code>(</code> e finalmente <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Displaying multiple times",
            "id": 129298,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Após capturar a entrada, podemos atribuí-la a uma variável e usá-la como qualquer outra variável.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;What's your name?&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"user_input = input()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Hi, \" /><text value=\"{user_input}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"!&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"37\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"What's your name?\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Mimo\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Hi, Mimo!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>user_input</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Prompt",
            "id": 129551,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos também adicionar um prompt adicional à função <code>input</code>. O prompt será exibido no console.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"user_input = input(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Enter your name: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"19\" endIndex=\"38\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Enter your name: \" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"Enter your name: \"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Output",
            "id": 129300,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Se inserirmos um prompt adicional, o usuário começará a digitar na mesma linha em que o prompt é exibido no console.</p><p>É por isso que é útil adicionar um espaço em branco no final do prompt usado na função <code>input</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"user_input = input(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Enter your name: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(f\" /><text value=\"&quot;Thanks, {user_input}!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Enter your name: Mimo\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Thanks, Mimo!\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
